  • C. Clark
    4.0 out of 5 starsVerified Purchase
    Works perfectly
    Reviewed in the United States on January 6, 2024
    Style: 1 remote + 3 outlets
    1.
    I bought these for my mother-in-law since her lights are those where you need to physically turn the switch next to the bulb. The remote is a game changer and reduces her fall risk at home. This way she does not have to lean over and risk falling to just turn the lights... See more
    I bought these for my mother-in-law since her lights are those where you need to physically turn the switch next to the bulb. The remote is a game changer and reduces her fall risk at home. This way she does not have to lean over and risk falling to just turn the lights on.

    The remote comes with a keychain attached to it and battery already installed. Therefore, you can hang the remote up somewhere or you can carry it with you, if you wanted to. The remote seems kind of fragile so I would not recommend carrying it around. There are two light bulb images at the top of the remote. The left bulb is shown as lit and the right bulb is shown as not being lit. These are supposed to resemble ON and OFF. Therefore, you need to press on the end of the button for whether you want to turn the outlet on or off and not on the middle of the button.

    The outlets are already preprogrammed so all you need to do is plug it in. To activate, you need to press the on/off button on the side of each outlet. Each outlet has a number on the back that matches the number on the remote. For instance, the #1, #2, and #3. That makes it easy to know which outlet you want to plug in at a certain area. There may be a slight delay when turning on/off but it is pretty negligible.

    I think these are excellent for people that are elderly, people that have hard to reach switches, or those that want the convenience of using a remote. However, I wish it came with two remotes. That way the remote is not carried between rooms. This is the biggest drawback I see at the moment.

    I am happy with this purchase and I would purchase these again for their convenience and ease of use.
